  "id": "PLACE_the_cinderwatch_ruins",
  "label": "The Cinderwatch Ruins",
  "description": "The Cinderwatch Ruins consist of shattered ferrocrete casemates and collapsed curtain walls strewn across an ash-limed saddle in Cyrenth Vale. Rift-born aurorae bruise the daylight, casting cold bands of color over scorched masonry and the stumps of void-hardened pylons. Broken transit culverts and half-buried conduit runs mark the site’s former integration into the planet’s sealed corridor network. Wind-driven fallout packs into firing slits and breached vault mouths, preserving the ruin as a permanent monument to siege and abandonment.",
